flowchart TD
    A([App mounts]) --> B{isAuthenticated?\npb.authStore.isValid}
    B -- No --> C[Render Auth form]
    C --> D[User enters email + password]
    D --> E[pb.authWithPassword]
    E -- Error --> F[Show error banner]
    F --> D
    E -- Success --> G[onAuthenticated → setAuthed=true]
    B -- Yes --> H
    G --> H[loadData triggered via useEffect]

    H --> I[authRefresh best-effort\nrequestKey: null]
    I --> J[initializeUser\nread orgId from pb.authStore.model]
    J -- No orgId --> K[Show org error, halt]
    J -- Has orgId --> L[Restore read state from localStorage\nRestore articles from sessionStorage]
    L --> M[Promise.all parallel fetch:\nvulnerabilities · weights · settings\nrssFeeds · groups · users]
    M --> N[Resolve weights: user → org default → hardcoded]
    N --> O[scoreVulnerability for each record]
    O --> P{lastKevSync stale?\n>24h or never synced}
    P -- Yes --> Q[syncKevFeed in background\nnon-blocking]
    P -- No --> R
    Q --> R{defaultFeedsSeeded?\nand no existing feeds?}
    R -- No --> S[Seed 3 default RSS feeds\nmark defaultFeedsSeeded=true]
    R -- Yes --> T[App ready]
    S --> T

    T --> U[pb.authStore.onChange listener]
    U -- Token expired / invalidated --> V[setAuthed=false]
    V --> C

    T --> W[User clicks Sign out]
    W --> X[logout → clear authStore\nreset all state]
    X --> C
